v3: %s/hwmon/xe_hwmon/
v4:
 - As power1_max_interval is rw attr take lock in read function as well
 - Refine comment about val to fix point conversion (Andi)
 - Update kernel version and date in doc
v5: Fix review comments (Anshuman)

